{"tid":2168252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金與正成北韓「第二把交椅」 南韓前總統幕僚：金正恩昏迷","createTime":"2020-08-21T15:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T15:59:50.000Z","uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77ab9b1d73ad20a89276fef1fb36dbf66ad1f0f0","tid":2168252,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"南韓情報機關表示，北韓最高領導人金正恩胞妹金與正，已成為北韓實際上的二把手，但不一定已獲指定為他的繼任人。<span class=\"red\">南韓前總統幕僚、金大中總統時代的青瓦台國情狀況室室長張誠珉引述中國消息指，金正恩早已昏迷不醒</span>，而北韓領導人除非病得很重或者政變被廢，否則不會下放權力，金與正獲權此舉證明金正恩病重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200821/T4OMXDI7SNAW3DB6KC3ULNTMIM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200821%2FT4OMXDI7SNAW3DB6KC3ULNTMIM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b506dc9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200821%2FT4OMXDI7SNAW3DB6KC3ULNTMIM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4ec2948d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200821/T4OMXDI7SNAW3DB6KC3ULNTMIM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"0ee3d60ce3febc0353113e1590a4a89d21d4c4d1","tid":2168252,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a829eecefac5616bfce0f76fdb28fadd2a8b1ca4","tid":2168252,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f907d35ff3682f0e4557f079eba6484128b06702","tid":2168252,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"